title: Chapter not exclusive
context: ยง514A-2 Chapter not exclusive. This chapter is in addition and supplemental to all other provisions of the Hawaii Revised Statutes; provided that this chapter shall not change the substantive law relating to land court property; and provided further that if this chapter conflicts with chapters 501 and 502, chapters 501 and 502 shall prevail.
